The paper deals with automated analysis of dermoscopy images, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The use of ensembles of thresholding methods suggests a machine learning approach, which is also relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR), multimedia (cs.MM), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI).
